306
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:12,040
Can you understand him?

307
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:12,720
Yes.

308
00:16:12,800 --> 00:16:14,160
Mr. Zhen Shuai teaches very well.

309
00:16:14,160 --> 00:16:15,240
I study very hard.

310
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:16,650
That's good.

311
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:21,200
I thought we wasted our money.

312
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:22,920
