326
00:16:45,040 --> 00:16:45,800
It's bad for your stomach.

327
00:16:45,800 --> 00:16:46,720
Auntie, you know what?

328
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:48,920
Mr. Zhen Shuai knows so much.

329
00:16:49,160 --> 00:16:51,020
