346
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:31,930
and absolutely won't let you down.

347
00:17:32,120 --> 00:17:33,920
College life is so interesting.

348
00:17:35,360 --> 00:17:36,360
There's a mosquito.

349
00:17:36,360 --> 00:17:37,620
Where is the mosquito?

350
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:39,680
Sit down and eat your food.

351
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:45,160
Really, Yuanbao?

352
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,810
Then you must work hard.

353
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:48,320
As long as you get into college,

354
00:17:48,320 --> 00:17:50,600
Auntie will buy you whatever you want.

355
00:17:51,040 --> 00:17:51,600
Really?

356
00:17:51,800 --> 00:17:54,400
Don't worry, I will burn the midnight oil,

357
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,240
study hard,

358
00:17:55,320 --> 00:17:56,560
