359
00:17:56,560 --> 00:17:57,690
and not let you down.

360
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:58,840
Good.

361
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:01,280
Come, Yuanbao, eat more.

362
00:18:01,520 --> 00:18:03,880
Good health gives you the motivation to study.

363
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:04,560
Exactly.

364
00:18:05,040 --> 00:18:07,700
I just like kids who get into good universities.

365
00:18:08,040 --> 00:18:08,760
Yuanbao,

366
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:11,460
you need to study hard with Mr. Zhen Shuai

367
00:18:11,640 --> 00:18:13,370
and get into a good university.

368
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:14,000
Right.

369
00:18:14,040 --> 00:18:14,640
Keep it up.

370
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:16,170
Grandpa is waiting for you.

371
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:17,920
Don't worry.

372
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:20,960
I feel that after Mr. Zhen Shuai's guidance this time,

373
00:18:21,160 --> 00:18:23,890
