374
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:25,130
As for my grades,

375
00:18:25,280 --> 00:18:26,080
I promise

376
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:28,840
I will definitely make even further progress.

377
00:18:29,040 --> 00:18:29,680
A UFO!

378
00:18:30,200 --> 00:18:32,200
