382
00:18:42,800 --> 00:18:43,960
You're so jumpy.

383
00:18:44,080 --> 00:18:46,480
Can you try to keep up with my studying pace?

384
00:18:46,680 --> 00:18:48,080
I advise you to take it easy.

385
00:18:48,080 --> 00:18:49,240
Don't brag too much.

386
00:18:49,440 --> 00:18:50,480
Yuanbao is right.

387
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:52,240
You need to learn from him.

388
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:53,320
Zhen Shuai, Zhen Shuai.

389
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:55,520
All you talk about all day is Zhen Shuai.

390
00:18:56,040 --> 00:18:56,760
Mom,

391
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:59,120
