402
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:31,400
What kind of enemy makes you so nervous?

403
00:19:32,120 --> 00:19:33,580
Are they stronger than me?

404
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:37,700
I'll tell you what.

405
00:19:37,880 --> 00:19:39,280
Go and see for yourself.

406
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:48,800
He's too strong.

407
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:50,960
Let's team up and take him down.

408
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:52,400
Why else would I call you?

409
00:19:53,040 --> 00:19:53,960
Mr. Zhen,

410
00:19:54,280 --> 00:19:57,600
