411
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:59,680
He's also an excellent student.

412
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:01,410
But I heard you are even better,

413
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:03,560
and he has some questions for you.

414
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:06,680
Would you mind teaching him as well?

415
00:20:06,720 --> 00:20:08,120
No problem. Don't worry.

416
00:20:08,320 --> 00:20:09,280
That's great.

417
00:20:09,560 --> 00:20:10,600
You guys go study.

418
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:12,760
I'll get you some water and fruit.

419
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:14,040
Thank you, Auntie.

420
00:20:14,040 --> 00:20:14,970
You're welcome.

421
00:20:15,320 --> 00:20:16,380
Thank you, Auntie.

422
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:18,320
Great, another top student.

423
00:20:18,800 --> 00:20:19,480
Let's go.

424
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:20,360
Go study now. Let's go.

425
00:20:20,360 --> 00:20:21,600
