430
00:20:31,840 --> 00:20:33,570
It will probably be on the test.

431
00:20:34,360 --> 00:20:35,080
Come.

432
00:20:35,320 --> 00:20:37,000
Don't just talk about the questions.

433
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:37,930
Have some water.

434
00:20:38,080 --> 00:20:39,080
Thank you, ma'am.

435
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:40,370
You're welcome.

436
00:20:40,440 --> 00:20:42,400
Mr. Zhen, thanks for your hard work.

437
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:44,260
It's nothing, ma'am. It's my job.

438
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:47,060
Come with me to get some fruit.

439
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:49,400
Yuanbao, help my mom get some fruit.

440
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:50,920
