446
00:21:10,360 --> 00:21:12,040
They shouldn't be on the college entrance exam.

447
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:12,680
Sir,

448
00:21:13,080 --> 00:21:14,340
our head teacher said,

449
00:21:14,480 --> 00:21:16,480
if this year's physics exam is easy,

450
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:18,000
next year's will be particularly hard.

451
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:20,130
Was your year's exam especially easy?

452
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,970
Let me take a good look, hold on.

453
00:21:32,520 --> 00:21:33,720
Eat the fruit.

454
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:35,280
Eat more fruit.

455
00:21:35,520 --> 00:21:37,450
I'll get you more when you're done.

456
00:21:38,360 --> 00:21:39,160
Study hard.

457
00:22:30,680 --> 00:22:32,640
I'll go get some more fruit.

458
00:22:37,600 --> 00:22:38,880
Sir, almost done?

459
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:42,480
Take a look.

460
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:43,440
This question

461
00:22:43,880 --> 00:22:45,410
should be solved like this.

462
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:15,800
Mr. Zhen,

463
00:23:16,280 --> 00:23:18,340
you seem to have calculated it wrong.

464
00:23:24,480 --> 00:23:25,320
Your

465
00:23:25,760 --> 00:23:26,880
seems wrong.

466
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:28,120
Sir,

467
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:30,440
