471
00:23:36,880 --> 00:23:37,760
We just wanted to see

472
00:23:37,760 --> 00:23:39,760
if you are a real teacher or a fake one.

473
00:23:39,760 --> 00:23:41,280
What if you lead students astray?

474
00:23:41,280 --> 00:23:42,210
What do you mean?

475
00:23:43,120 --> 00:23:45,250
Did you come here to test me on purpose?

476
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:46,720
We wouldn't dare.

477
00:23:47,280 --> 00:23:48,560
You are a top student,

478
00:23:49,040 --> 00:23:51,240
