484
00:24:02,640 --> 00:24:04,700
You won't get into college like this.

485
00:24:05,360 --> 00:24:07,120
Who are you saying won't get into college?

486
00:24:07,120 --> 00:24:08,920
What's with your attitude? I'm talking about you.

487
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:10,520
How can you curse someone not to get into college?

488
00:24:10,520 --> 00:24:11,560
I won't get into college?

489
00:24:11,560 --> 00:24:12,800
How could I not get into college?

490
00:24:12,800 --> 00:24:13,930
Who are you cursing?

491
00:24:14,880 --> 00:24:15,680
Mu Qingjun,

492
00:24:16,360 --> 00:24:17,420
what are you doing?

493
00:24:17,480 --> 00:24:18,560
Are you rebelling?

494
00:24:22,760 --> 00:24:24,760
The teacher said I can't get into college. He cursed me.

495
00:24:24,760 --> 00:24:25,360
Sit down.

496
00:24:26,720 --> 00:24:28,280
Sorry, Auntie.

497
00:24:28,520 --> 00:24:31,600
I just think his attitude towards studying is extremely incorrect.

498
00:24:31,600 --> 00:24:33,600
This will be very bad for his future.

499
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:36,200
You two make up.

500
00:24:45,480 --> 00:24:46,520
Let's start.

501
00:24:47,760 --> 00:24:49,000
I'm sorry.

502
00:24:50,040 --> 00:24:51,640
Love you.

503
00:24:53,320 --> 00:24:57,600
Because we are a family,

504
00:24:58,040 --> 00:25:01,920
a family that loves each other.

505
00:25:02,120 --> 00:25:04,480
It takes fate to bring us together,

506
00:25:04,760 --> 00:25:07,040
and heart to cherish each other.

507
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:11,840
Why let the clouds cover your eyes?

508
00:25:12,360 --> 00:25:15,080
Ms. Zhen, I am really sorry

509
00:25:15,800 --> 00:25:17,640
for putting you in a difficult position.

510
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:18,600
The children are still young.

511
00:25:18,600 --> 00:25:20,560
Please don't take it to heart.

512
00:25:21,040 --> 00:25:22,600
I will clean it up later

513
00:25:23,800 --> 00:25:25,130
and teach them a lesson.

514
00:25:25,720 --> 00:25:26,800
It's fine, Auntie.

515
00:25:27,120 --> 00:25:29,000
It was my fault today.

516
00:25:29,080 --> 00:25:30,140
I acted on impulse.

517
00:25:30,920 --> 00:25:32,480
I'll be going now.

518
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:33,440
Okay.

519
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:34,440
Ms. Zhen,

520
00:25:35,040 --> 00:25:36,680
I will call you later.

521
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:39,600
All right.

522
00:25:40,120 --> 00:25:41,000
Goodbye, Auntie.

523
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:42,200
Goodbye, Ms. Zhen.

524
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:44,280
Take care on your way.

525
00:25:45,080 --> 00:25:45,680
Goodbye.

526
00:25:54,760 --> 00:25:56,120
What's wrong with you today?

527
00:25:56,120 --> 00:25:58,050
Why did you almost get into a fight?

528
00:25:58,640 --> 00:25:59,480
No, Mom.

529
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:02,480
Well, I was a bit impulsive.

530
00:26:03,280 --> 00:26:03,960
But

531
00:26:04,440 --> 00:26:07,700
Mr. Zhen really doesn't know how to solve a lot of problems.

532
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:08,720
I guess

533
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:10,820
maybe because he went to college,

534
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:13,440
he forgot all the high school problems.

535
00:26:13,600 --> 00:26:15,530
He's not even as good as Meng Jingu.

536
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:19,160
He has been through it and is a top student.

537
00:26:19,280 --> 00:26:21,010
Can you be a little more humble?

538
00:26:23,040 --> 00:26:24,560
Auntie, how about this?

539
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:26,680
Let me tutor Yuanbao

540
00:26:26,680 --> 00:26:28,610
and Qingjun this summer vacation.

541
00:26:30,480 --> 00:26:31,880
I'm more familiar with them

542
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:33,240
and easier to get along with.

543
00:26:33,240 --> 00:26:33,880
Besides,

544
00:26:34,120 --> 00:26:35,960
we are learning the same grade's curriculum.

545
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:36,840
Every year's college entrance examination

546
00:26:36,840 --> 00:26:38,280
has a different focus.

547
00:26:38,520 --> 00:26:39,800
It's better to rely on ourselves than others,

548
00:26:39,800 --> 00:26:42,200
and it can also save you some money, Auntie.

549
00:26:43,600 --> 00:26:45,200
Jingu is such a good kid.

550
00:26:46,360 --> 00:26:47,960
So, do you two agree?

551
00:26:48,120 --> 00:26:48,800
I agree.

552
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:49,880
I agree.

553
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:52,340
All right, it's settled then.

554
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:54,560
Thank you for your hard work, Jingu.

555
00:26:54,560 --> 00:26:55,200
Great.

556
00:26:55,320 --> 00:26:57,120
The house will be much livelier.

557
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:01,480
Wait, Mom.

558
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:06,240
I don't think Meng Jingu needs to come for the whole summer vacation.

559
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:08,000
Right? Two days is enough.

560
00:27:08,560 --> 00:27:09,320
Not enough.

561
00:27:10,040 --> 00:27:11,500
Knowledge is systematic.

562
00:27:11,840 --> 00:27:14,770
I can come for the whole summer vacation, no problem.

563
00:27:15,520 --> 00:27:17,180
All right, it's settled then.

564
00:27:26,400 --> 00:27:27,520
I am really

565
00:27:28,200 --> 00:27:31,660
the mantis stalking the cicada, unaware of the oriole behind.

566
00:27:32,680 --> 00:27:33,480
Jingu.

567
00:27:35,280 --> 00:27:36,800
Look, what is this?

568
00:27:41,120 --> 00:27:43,760
Tickets to the opening ceremony of the Beijing Olympics.

569
00:27:43,760 --> 00:27:45,160
Haven't you always wanted to get into

570
00:27:45,160 --> 00:27:47,240
the Physics Department of Qingbei University?

571
00:27:47,240 --> 00:27:48,720
It just so happens that our family of three

572
00:27:48,720 --> 00:27:51,520
can take this opportunity to look around Beijing.

573
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:53,920
You can go to the Qingbei University you've been dreaming of,

574
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:54,760
to take a look.

575
00:27:55,000 --> 00:27:56,880
You're about to start your senior year.

576
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:58,480
Let's go out and relax a bit.

577
00:27:59,120 --> 00:28:00,760
And when we come back,

578
00:28:00,840 --> 00:28:02,880
you can devote yourself entirely to the college entrance exam.

579
00:28:02,880 --> 00:28:03,720
But...

580
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:05,240
What's wrong?

581
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:07,760
I've already agreed with my classmates

582
00:28:07,760 --> 00:28:10,320
to take extra classes together during the summer vacation.

583
00:28:10,320 --> 00:28:13,050
Do you still need extra classes with your grades?

584
00:28:13,640 --> 00:28:14,760
I'm acting as the tutor.

585
00:28:14,760 --> 00:28:15,600
Tutor?

586
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:16,840
Is it paid?

587
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:18,000
It's unpaid.

588
00:28:20,080 --> 00:28:21,000
Jingu.

589
00:28:21,160 --> 00:28:24,360
Look, your dad and I have already booked the tickets.

590
00:28:24,760 --> 00:28:26,920
Other students take tutoring classes anywhere.

591
00:28:26,920 --> 00:28:28,960
Besides, you're not a teacher.

592
00:28:29,080 --> 00:28:30,520
What kind of tutoring are you doing?

593
00:28:30,520 --> 00:28:32,680
This is our family of three's

594
00:28:32,760 --> 00:28:33,960
first trip together.

595
00:28:34,200 --> 00:28:37,320
How about you cancel the tutoring?

596
00:28:37,440 --> 00:28:38,440
All right.

597
00:28:39,120 --> 00:28:41,600
In the past, I always asked him to look up,

598
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:44,160
to only care about winning, losing, and profit,

599
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:45,620
instead of true feelings.

600
00:28:45,800 --> 00:28:47,960
But now I realize I was wrong.

601
00:28:48,680 --> 00:28:49,280
Dad.

602
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:51,860
You brat, you're still young.

603
00:28:52,520 --> 00:28:54,180
In the best years of your life,

604
00:28:54,840 --> 00:28:56,080
do what you want to do.

605
00:28:56,840 --> 00:28:58,480
Don't let the expectations of me and your mom

606
00:28:58,480 --> 00:28:59,280
hold you back.

607
00:28:59,440 --> 00:29:01,200
Never live for us.

608
00:29:01,520 --> 00:29:02,920
Be brave and be yourself.

609
00:29:05,440 --> 00:29:06,770
Why are you suddenly...

610
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:08,000
I am your father.

611
00:29:08,360 --> 00:29:10,000
And you are my son.

612
00:29:10,440 --> 00:29:11,840
I used to think,

613
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:14,080
what does a little kid like him know?

614
00:29:14,640 --> 00:29:16,440
But I've come to realize more and more

615
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:18,920
that sometimes he is also my teacher.

616
00:29:20,360 --> 00:29:21,440
You brat, you know what?

617
00:29:21,440 --> 00:29:22,520
Actually,

618
00:29:22,960 --> 00:29:24,520
it's also my first time being a dad.

619
00:29:24,520 --> 00:29:25,200
Maybe

620
00:29:25,280 --> 00:29:27,540
this dad is sometimes too authoritarian

621
00:29:27,840 --> 00:29:29,900
and rarely considers your feelings.

622
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:32,520
From now on, let's learn from each other.

623
00:29:32,840 --> 00:29:33,700
How about that?

624
00:29:34,080 --> 00:29:34,840
Thank you.

625
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:43,090
Are you really not going to tell Jingu?

626
00:29:46,320 --> 00:29:48,650
It's not certain that it's malignant yet.

627
00:29:48,840 --> 00:29:51,120
Telling him will only distract him.

628
00:29:52,160 --> 00:29:52,960
Forget it.

629
00:29:55,680 --> 00:29:57,040
I'll go to Beijing with you.

630
00:29:57,040 --> 00:29:58,970
We'll get it checked out properly.

631
00:30:32,360 --> 00:30:35,090
Yuanbao hasn't quite gotten the hang of science.

632
00:30:36,720 --> 00:30:37,580
Let me tell you.

633
00:30:38,440 --> 00:30:39,920
She actually works very hard,

634
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:41,080
but she tends to overthink things.

635
00:30:41,080 --> 00:30:42,210
She's too stubborn.

636
00:30:45,760 --> 00:30:48,600
She also has tons of embarrassing moments.

637
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:49,480
Let me tell you,

638
00:30:49,480 --> 00:30:50,200
over the years,

639
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:52,520
I've come to know all her strengths and weaknesses.

640
00:30:52,520 --> 00:30:53,000
Don't you think

641
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:54,320
I describe her perfectly?

642
00:30:54,320 --> 00:30:55,250
I'm telling you.

643
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:57,280
The other time she was in...

644
00:30:57,960 --> 00:30:59,720
Who are you saying is overthinking?

645
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:00,920
Who is overthinking?

646
00:31:01,560 --> 00:31:02,760
When did you get back?

647
00:31:03,400 --> 00:31:04,400
Don't just stare at me.

648
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:05,560
Who exactly likes to overthink?

649
00:31:05,560 --> 00:31:06,520
I do.

650
00:31:06,760 --> 00:31:08,220
I like to overthink, okay?

651
00:31:17,360 --> 00:31:19,560
Jingu, thanks for your hard work today.

652
00:31:19,640 --> 00:31:21,080
Be careful on your way home.

653
00:31:21,080 --> 00:31:23,000
Send me a message when you get home.

654
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:24,200
Don't worry, Auntie.

655
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:25,520
Then see you tomorrow.

656
00:31:25,520 --> 00:31:26,040
Okay.

657
00:31:26,320 --> 00:31:27,800
Then Auntie, Mutou,

658
00:31:28,080 --> 00:31:29,200
I'll be going back too.

659
00:31:29,200 --> 00:31:31,400
Okay, go to sleep as soon as you get back.

660
00:31:31,840 --> 00:31:32,520
Take it easy.

661
00:31:32,520 --> 00:31:33,080
Mom.

662
00:31:33,360 --> 00:31:35,000
Um, I'll walk them out.

663
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,890
Okay, make it quick. It's late.

664
00:31:38,280 --> 00:31:39,080
Okay.

665
00:31:42,040 --> 00:31:43,770
Desk mate, thank you for today.

666
00:31:44,360 --> 00:31:45,120
Don't mention it.

667
00:31:45,120 --> 00:31:45,320
Okay.

668
00:31:45,320 --> 00:31:46,400
Go back and rest early.

669
00:31:46,400 --> 00:31:46,640
Okay.

670
00:31:46,640 --> 00:31:47,600
I'll go back too.

671
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:49,400
See you tomorrow.

672
00:31:49,560 --> 00:31:50,560
See you tomorrow.

673
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:52,640
Hurry up and go sleep.

674
00:31:56,480 --> 00:31:58,440
Okay.

675
00:32:00,080 --> 00:32:01,080
See you tomorrow.

676
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:01,840
See you.

677
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:02,760
Definitely.

678
00:32:15,640 --> 00:32:17,600
Coming.

679
00:32:20,440 --> 00:32:21,280
Jingu.

680
00:32:21,360 --> 00:32:22,000
Auntie.

681
00:32:23,120 --> 00:32:24,180
You're back again.

682
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:27,200
Auntie, my house key is missing.

683
00:32:27,480 --> 00:32:28,640
I don't know if I forgot to bring it

684
00:32:28,640 --> 00:32:30,240
or left it in Qingjun's room.

685
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:32,000
Come on in.

686
00:32:32,080 --> 00:32:33,160
Let's look for it together.

687
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:34,000
Okay.
